              <oasis:line>3 </oasis:line>
            </oasis:entry>
            <oasis:entry colname="c4" valign="top">
              <oasis:line>That the said mortgagor, his heirs, executors, administrators, or some one of them, shall and will well and truly pay or cause to be paid unto the said mortgagee, his executors, administrators, or assigns, the said sum of money in the above proviso mentioned, with interest for the same as aforesaid, at the days and times and in manner above limited for payment thereof, and shall and will in everything, well, faithfully, and truly do, observe, perform, fulfil, and keep all and singular the provisions, agreements, and stipulations in the said above proviso particularly set forth, according to the true intent and meaning of these presents and of the said above proviso.</oasis:line>
